Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.49,Default,car,0,0,0,,Why'd you go after Mr. Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.49,通用720日文-ja,car,0,0,0,,なんで ネロさんを狙った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.30,Default,car,0,0,0,,Who put you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.30,通用720日文-ja,car,0,0,0,,誰の差金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.15,Overlap,av,0,0,0,,How'd you know it was Corteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.15,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なぜ コルテオだと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.00,Default,gat,0,0,0,,He leaked Nero's schedule to Fango,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.00,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,ネロさんの動きをファンゴに流していました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.92,Default,gat,0,0,0,,then came back to the Island yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.92,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,昨日もアイランドに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.75,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Then this man came to throw himself at our mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.75,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,それで がコルテオの情報を手土産に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.55,Default,bar,0,0,0,,with the info about Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.55,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,泣きついて来たって訳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.63,Default,gat,0,0,0,,The higher-ups want to work with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.63,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,上は あんたらと手を組みたがってます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:24.64,Default,gat,0,0,0,,With Fango gone, we're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:24.64,通用720日文-ja,gat,0,0,0,,ファンゴがいないと うちはもう終わりですから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.31,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:32.45,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You came to us from Orco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:32.45,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,お前 オルコんとこからうちに流れて来たんだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.55,Default,car,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm Carmelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.55,通用720日文-ja,car,0,0,0,,ええ カメロっす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.79,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Cut the half-assed crap. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.79,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,生温いことしてんじゃね 退け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.83,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Why'd you go after Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.83,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,何故 ネロを狙った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.11,Default,gan,0,0,0,,What were you and Fango planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.11,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ファンゴと何を企んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.79,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Was anyone else in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:54.79,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,他に仲間は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.04,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.04,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,なんとか言え
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.02,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.02,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうしようもねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Corteo needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.31,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,コルテオには死んでもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.01,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero, got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.01,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ネロ ちょっといいか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:21.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.56,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I've called the Fango family executives to meet with us in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:28.56,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,明日の朝 ファンゴ ファミリーの幹部連中を呼んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.40,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We'll talk with them then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.40,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,話をつけよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.37,Default,bar,0,0,0,,And about Corteo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.37,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,それで コルテオのことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.71,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Could you leave us alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.71,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,外してくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.39,Default,jon,0,0,0,,{\i1}The{\i0} Fango, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.39,通用720日文-ja,jon,0,0,0,,あのファンゴがね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.04,Default,tig,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.04,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,まだ 信じらんねよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.87,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey, Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.87,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,おぉ アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.52,Default,tig,0,0,0,,This is hard for you as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.52,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,おめぇもつれぇとこだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:03.40,Default,tig,0,0,0,,You've known Corteo a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:03.40,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,コルテオとは 付き合いなげぇんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.64,Default,av,0,0,0,,Has he said anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.64,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あいつ 何が話したか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.33,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.33,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,これが何一つ喋らね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.70,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Guess it'll take more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.70,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,まだまだ 掛かりそうだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:17.22,Default,john,0,0,0,,But at the rate he's going,\N Mr. Ganzo might just kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:17.22,通用720日文-ja,john,0,0,0,,でも あの様子だと ガンゾさんがやっちまいそうだですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:21.88,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He's got a real temper when it comes to Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:21.88,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,叔父貴はネロのことになると 頭に血がのぼるからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.66,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He might get carried away and—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.66,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,勢い余っ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.88,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.88,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,すまね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.06,Default,av,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.06,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.77,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Avilio, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.77,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ 俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.23,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I see... so he got caught, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.23,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そうか やっぱり捕まっちまったか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.04,Default,cer,0,0,0,,There's nothin' I can do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.04,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,俺に 何か出来ることねぇかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.68,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I... He...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.68,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,俺...あいつに...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.85,Default,av,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.85,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何があった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,Why did Corteo kill Fango?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.16,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何故コルテオがファンゴを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.65,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Fango betrayed Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.65,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,コルテオはファンゴに裏切られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.39,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Once he got the recipe from Scusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.39,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,スクーザからレシピを手に入れたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.51,Default,cer,0,0,0,,he said he didn't need him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.51,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,もう 用済みだってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.35,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Never in a million years would I've seen this comin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.35,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,まさか こんなことんなっちまうとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.02,Default,cer,0,0,0,,He's hated the mafia since he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:05.02,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ガキの頃から ずっとマフィアを毛嫌いをしてたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.54,Default,cer,0,0,0,,That's irony for you. No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.54,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,皮肉のもんだぜ マジで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.84,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,なんであいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:14.48,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Why'd he want to kill Nero so bad that he'd team up with Fango?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.48,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ファンゴと組んでまでネロをやろうとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.84,Default,cer,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who dragged {\i1}me{\i0} into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.06,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,お前が巻き込んだじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.09,Default,cer,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.81,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Hey! Someone get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.81,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,おい 誰か来てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.51,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Damn it. That little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.51,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,畜生 くそがき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.39,Default,gan,0,0,0,,In back! He escaped out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.39,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,裏だ 窓から逃げやって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.16,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,叔父貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.66,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Corteo escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.66,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,コルテオが逃げた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.69,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Head him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.69,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,回り込め
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.34,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,何かあったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.46,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.46,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.28,Default,gan,0,0,0,,That's what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.28,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,俺が聞きてぇぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.55,Default,gan,0,0,0,,This idiot just charged in out of\N nowhere and whipped out a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.55,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,突然このバカが銃突きつけてきやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.57,Default,bar,0,0,0,,He got away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.57,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,逃げられた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.77,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about that guy from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.77,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,端から気に食わねと思っていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.81,Default,gan,0,0,0,,You trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.81,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,くそが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.85,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,逃がすな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.13,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.38,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We've locked down all roads leading out of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.38,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,町から出る道は もう抑えてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.98,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.98,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.48,Default,bar,0,0,0,,About Avilio...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.48,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アヴィリオのことなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.92,Default,bar,0,0,0,,He and Corteo have known each other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.92,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,やつとコルテオは古い仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.96,Default,bar,0,0,0,,And he's covered for Corteo before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.96,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,それに 先もコルテオを庇うようなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.95,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I can't help but think—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.95,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,どうも俺には...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's because they're old friends from childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:07.98,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,それは 幼馴染みだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:12.57,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Barbero, you've got a habit of being too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:12.57,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,バルベロ 何でも疑い過ぎんのは お前の悪い癖だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.22,Default,nero,0,0,0,,First, we find Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.22,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まずは コルテオを見つけ出す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.36,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Everything else comes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.36,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ずべては そっからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:25.00,Default,av,0,0,0,,I see... If you find him, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:25.00,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そうか 見つかったら教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.92,Default,av,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.10,Default,av,0,0,0,,Corteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.10,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.57,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.57,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.05,Default,cor,0,0,0,,They're going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:50.05,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕は殺される...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.91,Default,cor,0,0,0,,If you don't kill Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.91,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,...君はネロを殺さないと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.48,Default,av,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.48,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,今どこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.05,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.05,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,明日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.38,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'll call you again at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.38,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,またこの時間に行っています
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:06.31,Default,cor,0,0,0,,If Nero's not dead by then, they'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:06.31,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その時までにネロが死んでないと 僕の命はない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.38,Default,av,0,0,0,,Who's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.38,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,誰といるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.35,Default,cor,0,0,0,,The one who sent you that letter is—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.35,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,あの手紙のお送り主は...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.43,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,たしか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.83,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Lagusa. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.83,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ラグーザとか言ったは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.58,Default,av,0,0,0,,You weren't alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.58,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,一人でじゃないような
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There were four of us, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.54,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おれを入れて四人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.91,Default,av,0,0,0,,There was one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.91,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,後 もう一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.02,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.37,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.81,Default,av,0,0,0,,You're taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.81,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,呑気なもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.61,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot like Fango.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.61,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺はファンゴみたいな間抜けじゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.62,Default,av,0,0,0,,Any trace of Corteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.62,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,コルテオの足取りは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.76,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.76,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まだつかめねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.90,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Some former bigwigs are meeting today to \Ntalk about where the family goes from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.90,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今日 主だったのが集まってファミリーの今後について話す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.30,Default,nero,0,0,0,,With Fango out of the picture, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.30,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファンゴの野郎もくたばったしなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.60,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You should come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.60,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前も立ち会え
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.09,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Uncle, how's the wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,叔父 傷はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.93,Default,gan,0,0,0,,It hurts a bit, but it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.93,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ちっとは痛むが大したことはねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.64,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Any word on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.64,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,それより あいつは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.16,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We haven't found him yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.16,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,まだ 見つかっていません
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.52,Default,bar,0,0,0,,but it's likely just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.52,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,時間の問題でしょうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.01,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.01,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,わざわざ呼び出してすまんな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.49,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.49,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,親父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:14.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I want Barbero to serve as a \Nfamily executive from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:14.08,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,バルベロには 今後ファミリーの幹部として働いてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:18.00,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don, I swear my loyalty to you anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:18.00,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ドン より一層の忠誠を誓います
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:22.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And this is Avilio Bruno, a new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:22.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,後 新しく入ったアヴィリオ ブルノ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.09,Default,vin,0,0,0,,The one with the booze?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.09,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,あの酒の?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's the one who brought it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あぁ こいつが持ち込んできた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's got a lot of moxie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なかなか根性が据ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.18,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Take care of Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.18,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ネロを頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.40,Default,av,0,0,0,,I will, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.40,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,分かりました ドン
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:46.86,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Children grow up before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:46.86,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,子供はいつの間にか大人になっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.38,Default,vin,0,0,0,,You do so much for them and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.38,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,あんだけ世話をしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.70,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Frate's dead and Fio's gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:53.70,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,フラテは死に フィオも去った
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:00.49,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Nero, I'm not blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:00.49,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ネロ お前を責めているわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:03.59,Default,vin,0,0,0,,You did it all to protect the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:03.59,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,すべてはファミリーを守るためだった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:10.60,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I thought welcoming Ronaldo into the family was the best way to protect it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:10.60,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,俺はぁ ロナルドを迎え入れることがファミリーを守る道だと考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:16.11,Default,vin,0,0,0,,and I listened to Ronaldo over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:16.11,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,そして お前ではなくロナルドの言葉を受け入れてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:21.10,Default,vin,0,0,0,,However that just made things worse with Frate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:21.10,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,だが それがフラテを増長させてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,In the end, Ronaldo was an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,結局 ロナルドは外の人間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.69,Default,vin,0,0,0,,That's right. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.69,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,そうだ 俺は間違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:34.47,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I was trying to do everything I could for the family as our don, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:34.47,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ドンとしてファミリーにとっての最善を尽くしたつもりだったが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.58,Default,vin,0,0,0,,It all came to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.58,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,なんてことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:40.05,Default,vin,0,0,0,,It was just the shallow thinking of a senile old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:40.05,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,耄碌爺の浅知恵だったというわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's enough. It's all in the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.16,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もういい すべて終わったことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.50,Default,vin,0,0,0,,If that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.50,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,あの子が...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:51.05,Default,vin,0,0,0,,If Frate hadn't died, the Galassias would never have stepped back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:51.05,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,フラテが死ななければ ガラッシアは黙っていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:55.63,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Nero, you did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:55.63,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,ネロ お前はやるべきことをやった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:01.84,Default,vin,0,0,0,,"God helps those who help themselves."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:01.84,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,自ら動かぬ者に天はその手を差し伸べず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.73,Default,vin,0,0,0,,Starting today, you sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.73,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,これからは お前がここに座るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.18,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,もうご存知かと思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:55.70,Default,bar,0,0,0,,As I believe you know,\N the Fango family is now incorporated into ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.70,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ファンゴ ファミリーがわれわれの傘下に入りました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.08,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,よって 今後は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:17:00.45,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Thus from now on, I'd like to reconsider\N the Island as a primary sales route,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.45,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アイランドを中心に 販売経路の見直し
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:04.66,Default,bar,0,0,0,,continue rebuilding while expanding the Lodge,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:04.66,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,再構築を進め 同時にロッジの規模を拡大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.38,Default,bar,0,0,0,,and work toward mass production.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.38,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,量産にも力を入れていきます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.17,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Then, regarding Lawless Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.17,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,なお ローレスヘブンについては
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.43,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I'd like to prepare to sell it in Chicago in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:14.43,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,近々 シカゴに卸す準備を始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.18,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Chicago? The Galassias won't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:18.18,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,シカゴ ? ガラッシアが黙ってねぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.01,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We'll negotiate with them, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.01,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もちろん話は通す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.32,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そこでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:28.13,Default,nero,0,0,0,,To that end, I'd like to send some to Don \NGalassia before the playhouse's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.84,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,劇場の杮落としで会う前に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:28.13,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,前もって 酒をドン ガラッシアに届けておきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.57,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.57,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アヴィリオ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.07,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Will you go in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.07,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺の代わりに行ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.78,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Wait, Nero. Let me handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.78,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,待ってネロ それなら俺が行く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.01,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Avilio's not ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.01,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,アヴィリオはまだ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No, we'll leave this one to Avilio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:38.76,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いや 今回はアヴィリオに任せる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.48,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺たちには劇場の準備があるしなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.48,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We have the preparations on the playhouse to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.61,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.61,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,やれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:44.89,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,頼んだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:51.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Dad, rehearsals are starting at the playhouse soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:51.34,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,親父 近々劇場でリハサールが始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Everything's in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,万事順調だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.74,Default,vin,0,0,0,,I see. I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.74,通用720日文-ja,vin,0,0,0,,そうか 楽しみにしてるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.07,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Wow, you're the don, Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.07,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ネロがドンかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:13.68,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You'll make a great don!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:13.68,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,大丈夫 お前ならきっとドンになれる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.32,Default,av,0,0,0,,Who was the man standing next to your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.32,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,親父さんの隣にいた男は誰なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Huh? You mean Del Toro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.27,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,デル トロの事か?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.33,Default,av,0,0,0,,I've never seen him speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.33,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,喋ってるのを見たこと無い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hear he got messed up in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.58,720通用注釋-ja,nero,0,0,0,,大概是第一次世界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:28.02,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,前の大戦でやられたそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:32.64,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The one in Europe. He's served\N under my dad ever since fighting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:32.64,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ヨーロッパでなぁ 戦ってた時から親父の部下だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.72,Default,av,0,0,0,,He's quite an old-timer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.72,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,相当な古株だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:39.65,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Wasn't he in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:39.65,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,あの人は確か務所に入ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, on a job for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.97,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファミリーの仕事でだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.93,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He got out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.93,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,そう で...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.35,Default,tig,0,0,0,,the year before last, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.35,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,一昨年だっけか 出てきたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,How long was he in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,どれくらい 入ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.89,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Not sure, five years or so, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:52.89,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,さぁな 五年かそこらだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.74,Default,av,0,0,0,,He went to prison seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.74,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,務所の入ったのは七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.07,Default,av,0,0,0,,Your first job... was that with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.07,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お前の初仕事も 一緒だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.48,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,いや 来ることになってたが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:06.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Nah. He was supposed to come along, but got sent to prison before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.82,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,その前務所に入っちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.80,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Gotta piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.80,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,小便だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.66,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.66,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,明日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.89,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'll call you again at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.89,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,また この時間に電話する
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:32.76,Default,cor,0,0,0,,If Nero's not dead by then, they'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:32.76,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その時にネロが死んでないと 僕の命はない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Uncle Ganzo thinks pretty highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.85,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ガンゾの叔父貴 随分お前のこと買ってるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.13,Default,av,0,0,0,,Does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.13,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そうなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:04.51,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He really pushed for me to take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:04.51,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あそこにお前を連れて行くのを だいぶ押してくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:10.04,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I was shocked. He's always been an old-fashioned kinda guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:10.04,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,驚いたぜ なんせ 昔気質のおじさんだからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:14.44,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I was sure he'd be the first to argue against it, but it was the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:14.44,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,真っ先に反対されるかと思ったら 逆だった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.73,Default,av,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.73,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.58,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'm glad your dad acknowledged you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.58,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,お前こそ 認められて良かったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.21,Default,av,0,0,0,,I'm pretty drunk. Going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.21,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,だいぶ酔った 先に帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.12,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That night, when Dad took me along on my first job...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.97,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,親父に初めて仕事に連れて行かれたあの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It wasn't just the kid who ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.08,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,逃げたガキだけじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.99,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I couldn't shoot anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.99,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,誰も撃つことが出来なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I was afraid to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,撃つのが怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I felt like Dad held me in contempt for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.27,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,親父に軽蔑された気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:09.33,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That's why I've thrown myself into my work to get him to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:09.33,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だから 親父に認めてもらう為に我武者羅にやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,A lot of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.66,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,殺してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.76,Default,nero,0,0,0,,And then, even Frate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:18.76,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そして フラテも...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:24.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,In the end, maybe nothing's really changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:24.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,結局 あの時からなん変わってねぇかもなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.09,Default,av,0,0,0,,But you could kill him now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.09,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,でも 今ならやれるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.11,Default,av,0,0,0,,That kid you failed to shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.11,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,七年前は撃ち損なった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:32.86,Default,av,0,0,0,,seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:32.86,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,そのガキを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.26,Default,av,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.26,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんただったんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.46,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Right answer, Angelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:41.46,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,正解だ アンジェロ
